occurrenceRemarks: No type designated in protologue: The material upon which this species is based was obtained from Dr. Leo Zehntner, who procured it at Sentocé, Bahia, Brazil. A box of living material, fruit, seeds, and several photographs of flowering plants were contributed by him. See USNH 762952 for supplementary material. USNH 762951 is mounted with material in packet possibly (re)moved from USNH 762952, which is annotated type and mounted with photographs but found in main herbarium without any specimen Feb. 2011 although something (as well as barcode) has clearly been forcibly removed from it; not inventoried but now placed in same folder with USNH 762951.
